t = [0, 1, 2, 3, 3, 4, 4, 4, 5]
pmf = Pmf.from_seq(t, normalize=False)
total = pmf.normalize()
self.assertAlmostEqual(total, 9)
self.assertAlmostEqual(pmf[3], 0.22222222)
cdf = Cdf.from_seq(t, normalize=False)
total = cdf.normalize()
self.assertAlmostEqual(total, 9)
self.assertAlmostEqual(cdf(3), 0.55555555)
